Change everything in my life has changed not all for the better
but i really wish it hadn't everyday i think back on those summer nothing to worry about nothing bad just me and my friends having the greatest time of our lives.
But now
Now that is gone my friends have moved away and now i'm the only one left, and not that i don't have new friends it's just that i miss my old ones.
I like to change things sometimes like my hair my clothes my nails my shoes, but the real thing is that's changing my appearance not my life my life is changing all the time and i have to live with that and i will i just wish sometimes i could say if i want something to change like is i want my friend to move away or if i want to hate the person i most want to be like, now it maybe seem like i can change my life the way i want it to but i can't i can't help hating the person i want to be most like but maybe that's why i hate her and i can't change my best friends moving away or just moving on.
I can't change, change.
but as change comes on i will get though it the good and the bad.

because my friends change is upon us and there is nothing to do about it!

Today i saw a boy he smiled at me and i smiled back.
Today i saw a girls she was pretty and sweet.
Today i saw myself living life the way i want.
Today i realized i have been living in fear.
Today i realized my life is nothing like the way i want it to be
Today i forgot everything bad in the world
Today i fell in Love.
Today i saw the world in a whole new way.
Today i started living.
Today is going to be a good day
Today i will be myself and no one else
Today is the day.
the day life begins.

She sites there
she just sites there
tucked in a ball
legs tight against her body
head down tucked away so no one can see it
arm's gripping her legs so tightly she can't move theme
crying so hard she can't breath
eyes red as blood
black tears flowing down her face
mascara all over her eyes
she sits there rocking back and forth
all alon in the darkness of her room
her mom and sister down stairs
not even know she is in her room falling apart
they go on living life as she sits alon in a dark room crying 
she grabs her necklace and holds the cross in her hand so tight she cuts herself and blood starts to flow from her hand
she looks to the sky and say
Lord help me through this 
all though i am alon
all though i am scared
she takes a deep breath
Help me please just help me
she puts her head back down and closes her eyes
she try's to stand up but she falls back to the floor she can't see 
tears have clogged her eyes
she curls back into a ball
and prays
she prays that she will be okay and ask's to help her through this
and then she closes her eyes again lays on the floor again
and fall asleep

I wish there was a pause button in life
so when ever something bad would happen you could just say pause and it would go away until you wanted to deal with it
A place where there is no crying no anger no hate just happiness 
And you don't have to worry about anything
but there is not such a place but it there was it would be great!

i need to stop thinking about this i need to stop thinking about him but i can't because it all over the news its all over everything everywhere i look i see it 
it wont go away it will never go away 
this feeling i have will always be here 
he will always be in my head even when i don't think he is
ill try to forget
but i never will

The it girl
Shes the one who gets noticed for nothing
shes the one who every one wants to be
shes the one with all the great ideas
shes the one with the great taste
she the one with all the friends 
shes the one who you would want for a daughter
All though  i'm pretty 
all though i'm the one the boys like
all though i have many things i want to do in life
They never matter as much as her
She has the great hair 
she has the nice smile
she can draw
she knows what she want and she know how to get it
as for me i stay here i stay in this place even though i'm drying even though i'm trying to get out i don't i can't
i don't ask for help 
i don't have many friends
i don't feel special
I feel alon 
i feel afraid
She has it all and more
i act like i do
even though i'm know where close
i am in this place watching the it girl
i wish i was the it girl
she has it all
i have goals and plans
I just don't tell anyone 
Because my plans will never even compare to the it girl
the it girl
she has it all
and as for me
i have what i need for the moment
i will be the it girl
even if it kills me
people will know who i am
even if that means leaving the person i was
even if that means leaving the person i want to be
the it girl 
just watch her shin
the it girl!
